## export

```{r save_ggplot}
save_ggplot = {

  ggsave(
    plot=ggpath,
    filename=file.path(imageFolder, "myPlot.svg"),
    width = 8,
    height = 5
  )
}
```

  * myPlot.svg及本Rmd檔一起上傳作業繳交處
